highlights.text: Fuerza Regida has the most spots on Top Songs Mexico. “Chula Vente” is the highest at #3.
“A Mí” by Rels B has been on Top Songs Mexico the longest, at 341 weeks straight.
“COMO OREO” by Blessd, Fuerza Regida, and Ovy On The Drums is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mexico at #83.
“Ansiedad” by Grupo Arriesgado is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mexico, up 58 spots at #80.
